WEBVTT

00:04.900 --> 00:05.900 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF, PBS NEWSHOUR
ANCHOR: Good evening.

00:05.900 --> 00:06.900 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
I'm Judy Woodruff.

00:06.900 --> 00:07.900 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
On the "NewsHour" tonight:

00:07.900 --> 00:09.966 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
(BEGIN VIDEO CLIP)

00:09.966 --> 00:11.100 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
DONALD TRUMP, PRESIDENT OF THE
UNITED STATES: The fundamental
question of our time is whether

00:11.100 --> 00:13.033 align:left position:25%,start line:86.67% size:75%
the West has the
will to survive.

00:13.033 --> 00:15.066 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(END VIDEO CLIP)

00:15.066 --> 00:18.666 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WOODRUFF: President Trump's
stark message in Poland --
signaling a fight to preserve

00:18.666 --> 00:23.666 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
Western civilization,
a day before meeting
Russian President Putin.

00:25.666 --> 00:29.100 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Then, retail giant Hobby Lobby
agrees to pay $3 million and
return thousands of smuggled

00:31.633 --> 00:36.300 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Iraqi artifacts, as the
company's devout Christian
president plans to open
a museum of the bible

00:38.200 --> 00:41.000 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
just blocks from the
nation's capitol.

00:41.000 --> 00:46.000 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
And -- a salute to the
father of rock 'n' roll.

00:47.900 --> 00:52.266 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
A new album showcases
Chuck Berry's enduring
influence on American music.

00:53.033 --> 00:55.066 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
