in Washington, D.C. that
will open this fall.

21:17.466 --> 21:19.566 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
For more on this case, I'm
joined now by Deborah Lehr.

21:19.566 --> 21:23.766 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
