21:39.233 --> 21:44.233 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DEBORAH LEHR, FOUNDER,
ANTIQUITIES COALITION:
The government is alleging
that they imported

21:46.700 --> 21:49.400 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
