permits to be able to
bring these antiquities
into the country.

22:01.000 --> 22:02.400 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
BRANGHAM: And what
are these antiquities?

22:02.400 --> 22:04.500 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
