we're talking about?

22:04.500 --> 22:09.500 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
LEHR: They are things, as you
said, that are destined for
their biblical museum, and they

22:11.466 --> 22:14.766 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
