33:17.000 --> 33:19.533 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
I am not a burden
on the community.

33:19.533 --> 33:22.800 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
I am not a burden
on social services.

33:22.800 --> 33:27.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
