refugees do the same.

33:31.733 --> 33:36.733 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
SOLMAN: So, are refugees the
economic boon that motivated
immigrants famously have been?

33:38.233 --> 33:41.533 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Yes, says economist Jeffrey
Sachs, but there are negatives.

33:41.533 --> 33:45.333 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY SACHS, ECONOMIST,
COLUMBIA UNIVERSITY:
Some workers face
increased job competition

33:45.333 --> 33:47.833 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
