owners may see more workers
at lower cost for them.

34:01.233 --> 34:06.000 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
SOLMAN: And what if, as
many Americans fear, even
just a few are terrorists?

34:06.866 --> 34:09.833 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
