the most intensively
screened immigrants
really to come to this

34:18.600 --> 34:23.600 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
country, about two years
of intense scrutiny
by the Department of
Homeland Security, the

34:25.633 --> 34:29.300 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
