35:03.666 --> 35:08.633 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Yousif al Saad went to work
at the Chobani yogurt plant
outside Utica, whose CEO, Hamdi

35:11.033 --> 35:16.033 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Ulukaya, has championed
the rights of refugees and
hired hundreds of them.

35:18.033 --> 35:22.166 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
