36:03.900 --> 36:08.300 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
SOLMAN: But the sexual assault
by minors is shrouded in
secrecy, and the TB case spike

36:10.333 --> 36:14.300 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
