mile area that included twin

36:16.200 --> 36:20.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
falls, none of the cases
contagious, none involving
Chobani employees.

36:20.800 --> 36:22.033 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
JONES: This isn't
some game people.

36:22.033 --> 36:23.566 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
