and defamatory reports.

36:34.066 --> 36:36.233 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
JONES: And I'm ready
to take them on.

36:36.233 --> 36:37.566 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Christ, please help us win this.

36:37.566 --> 36:39.566 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
