36:39.566 --> 36:41.833 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
SOLMAN: The following
month, Jones issued an
apology and a retraction.

36:41.833 --> 36:46.833 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JONES: On behalf of Info Wars, I
regret that we mischaracterized
Chobani, its employees

36:48.166 --> 36:50.233 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
