pushing companies to increase

39:09.566 --> 39:11.566 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
culture and diversity.

39:11.566 --> 39:15.966 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Kapor Klein and her husband
